        {
            "title": "台灣利率市場：10年殖利率大幅下滑 標售優預期；短期利率持平區間",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 台灣央行在午間公佈10年期公債標售利率低於預期，結果出爐後殖利率隨之走跌一度觸及1.49%，為同年期熱券的近兩個月最低；終場收低3.25基點至1.495%，跌破標售利率。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣10年公債得標利率1.505%低於預期 銀行比重創一年半最大</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國票證券債券交易員Tim Yu受訪表示，銀行為了消化資金積極競標；之前央行總裁楊金龍的態度對於通膨並沒有很擔心，而且近日台幣升值，有助於緩解輸入性通膨</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今天標售後殖利率走低，應該是因為一些空單回補；預期在籌碼被銀行鎖住後，殖利率往上或往下的空間都不大</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貨幣市場</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f91464e1-5b36-3419-9224-32488d4d1758-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據票券商與銀行人士稱，周二資金供需大致平穩，銀行多數都已回補積數，在市場上找錢不難，短票與拆款利率維持在近日區間。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據一位銀行資金調度人士稱，銀行同業多數都已回補積數，但還沒有急於消化餘錢的壓力；外商銀行的資金多缺不一</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前拆出一周給銀行在1.25%，持平近日水準</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據兩位票券商人士表示，雖然有些銀行運用較保守，整體資金供應算是充裕，賣票與拆款操作順暢</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與銀行承作約30天期自保短票主要在1.46%-1.47%，同上日</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">跨月拆款利率在約1.40%-1.41%</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述交易員不願具名接受採訪，因未被授權公開評論</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣短票市場：30天自保票上交易日平均利率1.463%</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場動態</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博追蹤櫃買中心數據，10年熱券成交在1.495%，跌3.25基點；成交3億元台幣</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5年熱券電子盤無成交</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台股加權指數上漲1.8%，報37605.11點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台北時間下午1:34，據彭博數據，5年期利率交換報2.07%，跌1基點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國10年期國債殖利率紐約尾盤報4.251%，亞洲盤中報4.2421%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台北時間下午12:00，據拆款中心數據，隔夜拆款加權平均利率在0.823%，區間在0.805%-0.825%，上日收在0.826%</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2-7天平均利率在1.257%，區間在1%-1.41%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上交易日當日超額準備為111億元台幣；本提存期累計超額準備為8042億元台幣，加計前期1%超額準備為1兆1948億元台幣</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至上交易日，央行定存單未到期餘額為7兆965.4億元台幣，上日減發125.1億元</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">重點關注</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普稱停火期不太可能延長 施壓德黑蘭達成和平協議</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">WTI原油期貨亞洲時段下跌 因伊朗料將參加談判</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會主席候選人沃什：若提名獲得確認 將堅決捍央行獨立性</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">[深度] 主張聯儲會亟需「政權更替」 沃什提名確認聽證會有哪些看點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國銀行建議買入美國國債曲線中段 料受益於降息押注升溫</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-10%E5%B9%B4%E6%AE%96%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91-%E6%A8%99%E5%94%AE%E5%84%AA%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E7%9F%AD%E6%9C%9F%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E6%8C%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8D%80%E9%96%93-060228992.html",
