        {
            "title": "IPO火爆助中國金融業跑贏製造業 為數年來首次",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"National Bureau of Statistics\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"665\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IG.LAXYRhNeGk.nsCP_oCg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/434a85dbea94c64fb287d87bde0bed14\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">National Bureau of Statistics</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在中國經濟超預期反彈的第一季度，得益於火熱的募股籌資活動，其金融業增速數年來首次超過了製造業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國家統計局上周公佈的數據顯示，一季度GDP同比成長5%，而增速快於整體經濟的行業包括金融業和製造業，它們分別成長了6.5%和6.3%。相比之下，酒店和餐飲等對消費更為敏感的行業增速放緩。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"665\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3B73QDsS7M.sdEpR1ZDjPw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a3f725cfcabe93b8ffd641c9ac86e3d0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">涵蓋保險、銀行以及證券等多個領域的金融業，增速在2025年底連續兩個季度放緩後，回升至新冠疫情爆發以來的最高水平。2026年首次公開募股(IPO)激增加上股票交易火爆，提升了金融業的活動水平；該行業規模不足中國製造業的三分之一。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-581eba1c-2bb3-3d2f-9af7-b92880f66bde-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在中東爆發戰爭的背景下，投資者尋求避險，而中國抵禦全球石油衝擊的能力更加卓越，使得中國股市表現排在了全球前列。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這也促使一季度中國A股日均成交量飆升。彭博新聞社匯編的、可追溯至2010年的數據顯示，成交量在1月中旬創下紀錄高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">官方媒體《上海證券報》報導稱，一季度A股完成上市發行的公司共計30家，IPO募資規模達到258.79億元，同比成長近六成。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Chinese Manufacturing Growth Overtaken by Finance Amid IPO Boom</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jiyeun Lee、Amanda Wang.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/ipo%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%A5%AD%E8%B7%91%E8%B4%8F%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD-%E7%82%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1-060221133.html",
